\p 
\v 5 \w My|strong="G3739"\w* friends, \w I|strong="G3739"\w* \w have|strong="G2532"\w* something \w to|strong="G2443"\w* \w tell|strong="G3568"\w* \w you|strong="G4771"\w*. \w We|strong="G3739"\w* \w have|strong="G2532"\w* \w to|strong="G2443"\w* love each \w other|strong="G3739"\w*. \w You|strong="G4771"\w* already \w know|strong="G3568"\w* \w that|strong="G2443"\w*. \w We|strong="G3739"\w* heard \w that|strong="G2443"\w* message \w from|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* beginning, \w right|strong="G3756"\w* \w from|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w time|strong="G3568"\w* \w you|strong="G4771"\w* first heard \w about|strong="G5613"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G2532"\w*. \w It|strong="G2532"\w*’s \w the|strong="G2532"\w* message \w that|strong="G2443"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G2532"\w* told us.\x * \xo 1:5 \xt John 13:34; 15:12, 17\x*
