\s1 Watch out for people that are telling lies about Jesus
\p 
\v 7 \w You|strong="G3754"\w* see, \w there|strong="G2532"\w* \w are|strong="G1510"\w* lots \w of|strong="G2532"\w* \w people|strong="G4561"\w* \w that|strong="G3754"\w* \w say|strong="G2532"\w* \w they|strong="G2532"\w* \w are|strong="G1510"\w* telling \w people|strong="G4561"\w* \w God|strong="G2532"\w*’s message, \w but|strong="G2532"\w* \w they|strong="G2532"\w* \w go|strong="G1831"\w* around telling lies \w about|strong="G1722"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G2424"\w*. \w Those|strong="G3588"\w* \w people|strong="G4561"\w* \w say|strong="G2532"\w*, “\w Jesus|strong="G2424"\w* \w Christ|strong="G5547"\w* \w did|strong="G2532"\w* \w not|strong="G3361"\w* \w come|strong="G2064"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w live|strong="G2532"\w* \w as|strong="G1519"\w* \w a|strong="G2532"\w* \w human|strong="G4561"\w* \w being|strong="G1510"\w* \w here|strong="G1510"\w* \w on|strong="G1722"\w* \w earth|strong="G4561"\w*.” \w Those|strong="G3588"\w* \w people|strong="G4561"\w* \w are|strong="G1510"\w* proper liars. \w They|strong="G2532"\w* \w are|strong="G1510"\w* enemies \w of|strong="G2532"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G2424"\w* \w Christ|strong="G5547"\w*.
